TODAY ONLY! Kick off the weekend with a treat! 🍩🍩 $13 double dozen this Friday the 13th! 🎉 Online or in shop! In-shop purchases require bar-code found at link in bio.

Participating US shops, redeemable for 8/13 only. In shop purchases require bar-code. Valid for 2 Dozen Original Glazed or 1 Dozen Original & 1 Dozen Classic Assorted. All info at link in bio. #krispykreme #doughnuts

Looking for a treat to make this Friday the 13th sweet? Pre-order 2 dozen doughnuts online for only $13, for this Friday only! 🎉🍩

Participating US shops, redeemable for 8/13 only. Valid for 2 Dozen Original Glazed or 1 Dozen Original & 1 Dozen Classic Assorted. All info at link in bio. #krispykreme #fridaythe13th #doughnuts

Participating US shops only, through 8/11 - order now at the link in our bio. #krispykreme #doughnuts

Participating US & CAN shops. All info on doughnuts & shops found at link in bio
